Text0_0_loc7='The humans built an inn on the edge of the Barrens. The Shady Rest, they called it. Weeks ago, it was burned down.$B$BThe Warchief told us to leave the humans alone, so long as they didn\'t cross our borders, but it appears someone violated his wishes.$B$BHe has put me in charge of getting to the bottom of it. If you wish to provide assistance, go to the remains of the Shady Rest Inn and return any clues you find to me.'
