UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc7='Och! Ye seek training in the way of the warrior, do ye?  Kelstrum Stonebreaker will put ye through yer paces!  Just march yerself over to the Hall of Arms east of the gates of Ironforge.',Text0_1_loc7='Och! Ye seek training in the way of the warrior, do ye?  Kelstrum Stonebreaker will put ye through yer paces!  Just march yerself over to the Hall of Arms east of the gates of Ironforge.',Text1_0_loc7='Kelstrum is a loudmouth and a braggart... and if that weren\'t enough he\'s also one of the most skilled warriors ye\'ll ever meet!  $B$BI tell ye, if ye\'re looking to be trained in the ways of a warrior, that\'s who ye should be talking to.  I\'m sure he can be found over in the Hall of Arms east of the Gates of Ironforge.',Text1_1_loc7='Kelstrum is a loudmouth and a braggart... and if that weren\'t enough he\'s also one of the most skilled warriors ye\'ll ever meet!  $B$BI tell ye, if ye\'re looking to be trained in the ways of a warrior, that\'s who ye should be talking to.  I\'m sure he can be found over in the Hall of Arms east of the Gates of Ironforge.' WHERE entry=2776;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc7='The tinkerer\'s craft for you is it?  No doubt ye\'ll want to go see Springspindle Fizzlegear in Tinker Town.  $B$BJust head east from the gates of Ironforge, or follow the sound of the explosions.',Text0_1_loc7='Oh, you\'re looking for Springspindle Fizzlegear then.  Why that little gnome and his gadgets...  Let me tell you, if you\'re going to his shop in Tinker Town, keep your hands to yourself and don\'t pet any of his mechanical sheep!  $B$BExploding sheep... now why would you even make such a thing!?',Text1_0_loc7='Oh, you\'re looking for Springspindle Fizzlegear then.  Why that little gnome and his gadgets...  Let me tell you, if you\'re going to his shop in Tinker Town, keep your hands to yourself and don\'t pet any of his mechanical sheep!  $B$BExploding sheep... now why would you even make such a thing!?',Text1_1_loc7='Oh, you\'re looking for Springspindle Fizzlegear then.  Why that little gnome and his gadgets...  Let me tell you, if you\'re going to his shop in Tinker Town, keep your hands to yourself and don\'t pet any of his mechanical sheep!  $B$BExploding sheep... now why would you even make such a thing!?' WHERE entry=2798;
