Text0_0_loc7='The ravasaur here in Un\'Goro seem to be related to the raptors of the barrens--highly intelligent, volatile, and with a sense or code of conduct. The greatest of these that I have encountered is  Lar\'korwi. He is one of the most dangerous beasts I\'ve ever seen. In taurahe, Lar\'korwi means sharp claw, but that does not do him justice.$B$BDo not underestimate Lar\'korwi if you ever plan on hunting him, but I will help you in any way I can if you do.'
