Text0_0_loc7='Welcome to the Wickerman Festival, $C!$B$BOn the observance of Hallow\'s End, the Forsaken burn a wickerman in honor of this, the most revered of occasions.  It was on this day that the Banshee Queen herself delivered us from the clutches of the Lich King and the Scourge.  We have remained free ever since.  Those who would have seen us fall are repaid in full... with vengeance!$B$BThe burning of the Wickerman begins at 8:00 PM!',Text0_1_loc7='Welcome to the Wickerman Festival, $C!$B$BOn the observance of Hallow\'s End, the Forsaken burn a wickerman in honor of this, the most revered of occasions.  It was on this day that the Banshee Queen herself delivered us from the clutches of the Lich King and the Scourge.  We have remained free ever since.  Those who would have seen us fall are repaid in full... with vengeance!$B$BThe burning of the Wickerman begins at 8:00 PM!'
