Text0_0_loc7='Well now, I\'m surprised to see other adventurers in a place such as this! If I\'d known you were comin\' I woulda tagged along with ye instead o\' flying this infernal gnomish contraption. Now that you\'re here through, ye can help me get to the Tribunal! If my research theories about these halls is correct, information pertainin\' to the creation o\' the entire dwarven race lies within!'
